description: This top 10% Plezier purrs with a rating of 50, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 150, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Leverage for North, 1 for East, 3 for South, and Nine Lives for West. Plezier has the personality suit of yenta. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Plezier [150 Votes, Top 10%]
